</head>
<p>Gorgas details the yearly deaths caused by yellow fever in the month of July, and states that the sanitary conditions for July 1900 are better than any time in the past ten years. His report includes two charts of deaths in Havana: &ldquo;Deaths by Months for the Years 1890 to 1900&rdquo; and &ldquo;Arrivals and Departures of Passengers at Havana.&rdquo;</p>
</div1>
